Capture 2.0 >>> A Tool for the Network Monitoring

REQUIRES

libmicrohttpd >=0.3
rrdtool >= 1.3.8

BUILDING

cd capture
make all

EXECUTION

./capture -h				# display helps
sudo ./capture -d en1		# start capture on en1 network interface
sudo ./capture -d en1 -r	# enable RRDTOOL

DUMP

http://localhost:19999/counters		# display counters json on your browser
http://localhost:19999/flows		# display flows json on your browser